meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN MONTH ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) IN ( 10 , 11 , 12 ) THEN YEAR ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) || ' - Q1' WHEN MONTH ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) IN ( 1 , 2 , 3 ) THEN YEAR ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) || ' - Q2' WHEN MONTH ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) IN ( 4 , 5 , 6 ) THEN YEAR ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) || ' - Q3' WHEN MONTH ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) IN ( 7 , 8 , 9 ) THEN YEAR ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) || ' - Q4' ELSE NULL END AS "#{\"EKKO\".\"AEDAT\"}" FORMAT "%Y-%m"
